  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThis is what I see for about 20 minutes when changing password. I suppose there's a database re-encryption runs in the background, but we definitely need some UI for this process.\r\n![Screenshot 2023-07-05 at 19 02 41](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/25482501/70010656-c60e-4821-8637-82a34d1feb41)\r\n\r\nAlso a minor thing: password changed popup looks a bit broken:\r\n<img width=\"1312\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/25482501/f2bce260-5179-41df-9b09-9a02d1596c28\">\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nUI:\r\n- doesn't freeze\r\n- asks the user not to close the app (because it will break the database)\r\n- prior changing the password gives a warning that it might take a while\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nUI freezes for 20 minutes or so.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.13-rc5\r\n- Operating System: MacOS 13.4 (22F66)\r\n\r\n",
